data.description: Welcome to your West Palm Beach paradise! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem features a fully renovated interior and an incredible backyard with a sparkling pool. With a 2-car garage and a newer roof, this property is both stylish and practical. Enjoy the Florida lifestyle to the fullest in this dreamy home!This attached single family, situated in the heart of Coconut Grove, offers three bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, and was constructed in 2006.
